name: PLEASE FASTEN SEAT BELT WHEN SEATED.
description: This is my first collab with a musician @anvita_shankar , she is a sitar player she is a student of this ancient art. I asked her to compose a piece for me and what that piece would make me feel I would draw. So here it’s is what I felt. This was a very interesting exercise of translating music onto paper I enjoyed it and it made me push my limit of what is creativity. It was quite instant to pick up a note of romance and intimacy on the song she composed maybe it’s just me who perceived it like that. dimensions 1920 x 1080 size 48.6
